				<p>Expand your editing set up with Thunderbolt So I&#8217;m thinking of upgrading my trusty MacBook Pro later next year, but it only comes with 2 USB 3.0 ports and 2 Thunderbolt ports and an HDMI port. So I&#8217;ve already begun &hellip; <a href="http://jonnyelwyn.co.uk/thunderbolt/the-best-thunderbolt-expansion-peripherals-for-editors/" >Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	
